result.title: The Santa Claus Brothers Special (Starring Bryan Cranston as Santa)
result.description:
With Bryan Cranston as the voice of Santa...what’s under the tree isn’t the only surprise you’re in for this holiday season. You are about to learn the North Pole’s best kept secret…

Santa Claus has three sons. And there’s a reason why they aren’t in charge of Christmas.
